                        <h1>Total Cost of Ownership &ndash; A Guide for Commercial Vehicle Fleets</h1>
                        <p xmlns="">
                            <img class="imgFloatLeft" title="Mobil Delvac&trade; Products" src="../uk-english-lcw/Images/TCO_guide_image.PNG" height="150" width="150" alt="Mobil Delvac&trade; Products" align="left" border="0" hspace="0"></p>
                        <p xmlns="">Total Cost of Ownership (TCO) of a truck is often discussed, but calculating the true TCO of different vehicles can be a complicated task.</p>

                        <p xmlns="">Essential to managing a fleet&rsquo;s bottom line, TCO takes into account all costs associated with owning a vehicle.</p>

                        <p xmlns="">From purchase to disposal, and everything in between, it enables owners to manage finances and make efficiencies where possible by understanding the full picture of costs.</p>

                        <p xmlns="">As restrictions and regulations on heavy duty vehicles continue to ramp up, cost control has never been more important for commercial fleets.</p>

                        <p xmlns="">We&rsquo;ve produced a guide to help you navigate the TCO of your fleet. It covers the fundamentals of TCO and practical advice on how you can help reduce it.</p>

